                <li style="display: none; width: 100%;" class="slide-556 ms-image"><img width="466" height="621" src="http://localhost/crst.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/equinox-business-cards.jpg" class="slider-554 slide-556" alt="Tim Rifkin Business Card" height="250" width="250" rel="" title="Tim Rifkin Business Card" srcset="http://localhost/crst.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/equinox-business-cards.jpg 466w, http://localhost/crst.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/equinox-business-cards-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 466px) 100vw, 466px" /></li>
